jsondiscoverer.web

Class FeedbackServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • jsondiscoverer.web.AbstractJsonDiscoverer
          • jsondiscoverer.web.FeedbackServlet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    @WebServlet(value="/feedback")
public class FeedbackServlet
extends AbstractJsonDiscoverer
    Servlet to provide support for receiving feedback

    Answers to POST calls, receiving as input a comment and the JSON document that triggered the feedback. Optionally the images for metamodel/model can also be attached

    Author:
    Javier Canovas (me@jlcanovas.es)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
